pageTitle: UKC Logbook - Yzeron (rochers de Py froid)
textBeforeTable: Upload a file of missing climbs Add missing Climb   Left to Rightby Nameby Gradeby TicksReverse Sort climbs Climbs at this crag Guidebooks Escalade autour de Lyon (2007) Head to Yzeron, at Yzeron drive through the main square and take the road Les Charmottes (which will drive you past a modern monastery on your left). Once past the monastery take the second left up Envers de Py Froid. Park at the top of the hill (safe, multiple spaces). Follow the signs on foot to Les Rochers Py Froid (1.6km). You will arrive at a large green space which is marked by a black triangle/splodge on the map.
